# 1️⃣8️⃣ PRIVACY and DATA PROTECTION BALANCE

While ensuring traceability:

* Sensitive personal data masked when necessary
* Access to personal metadata controlled
* Logs encrypted at rest

Maintains data protection compliance.

---

# 1️⃣9️⃣ COMMON FAILURE POINTS TO AVOID

❌ Logs editable by administrators
❌ No version tracking
❌ No device/IP logging
❌ No time synchronization
❌ No linkage across modules
❌ Log overwriting instead of append-only
❌ Audit logs stored in same table as operational data

